{"tid":475771,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"乜野叫work life balance?","createTime":"2017-11-21T12:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T17:02:27.000Z","uid":101935,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"16b0bedfe8a9aeee50950d24f552d7c5d06d8a44","tid":475771,"uid":101935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T12:08:24.000Z","msg":"一朝起身趕頭趕命 逼巴士逼地鐵 全車人塊面有幾黑得咁黑<br />\n落車行入面包店買個空氣包 閒閒地都6-7蚊<br />\n唔緊要啦買個狗吃早餐都係為左填飽個肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到公司門口帶番個面具準備上樓對住班濕鳩同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n開工喇 做做做 一路做就一路比senior屌 一係就比同事冼穫金<br />\n自己一路冇停過手就望住D老屎忽鳩fingfing吹下水笑笑下又幾個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好喇放飯 攰到拿拿聲食完就訓幾個字 捱埋個下午就收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n6點收工再逼巴士逼地鐵 排下隊又塞下車 上到車好快就恰著左 番到屋企7點幾8點<br />\n坐低冇耐就有屋企飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n食飽撳下電話上下網 哇望下個鐘已經就快十一點<br />\n沖埋個涼搞呢搞路就差唔多要訓覺準備再loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"620473652b92baa77a67ab29ebd2b85aedd5bc39","tid":475771,"uid":158998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T12:10:17.000Z","msg":"搵過第二份工"},{"pid":"545de5c0d387606c037c90b8738407558eae4db8","tid":475771,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T12:22:45.000Z","msg":"兩邊都做到隻狗咁夠晒balance"},{"pid":"537ebac4039ae5b90f55fafdf2e75c2a8be007e0","tid":475771,"uid":78089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T12:26:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12fa9d1220350e1d23e84a64efd9c4c879beaf3e","tid":475771,"uid":21861,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T12:35:28.000Z","msg":"樓主你就好 有得六點收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce16e22e406eb798d3e1010dcf8887b0e39aa0ee","tid":475771,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:13:38.000Z","msg":"返一放二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6544c2b913269b29b2888b5498ae33e88dd1ed7e","tid":475771,"uid":87337,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:18:27.000Z","msg":"試下早啲出門口，坐低食個早餐<br />\n全日感覺都會冇咁灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c209a65b8a5009e32ec027d626d90998972880f","tid":475771,"uid":51066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:32:52.000Z","msg":"sleep is for the weak <br />\n就解決到唔多夠時間問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7900aac458595d4227da0f4d6111bd0c6df2400","tid":475771,"uid":54387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:33:35.000Z","msg":"提早退休啦"},{"pid":"fa0615b2a9c89bb2d9f067593b99f9a4a33fd84a","tid":475771,"uid":55198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:41:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> hong kong<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e15a2b34591e86a12805787b7001b599f89cf38b","tid":475771,"uid":36030,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:46:42.000Z","msg":"6點半起身<br />\n7點20分出門口<br />\n8點到公司  開電腦 沖咖啡 歎早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n8點半開始做野  要做既野唔多  耐唔耐先要覆次email<br />\n12點正叮飯  食完同同事吹水吹到1點半，又或者出去商場行下<br />\n1點半沖咖啡  一路hea一路做<br />\n4點45分去定廁所<br />\n5點正即閃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返到屋企做一個鐘運動<br />\n煮飯、食飯、準備聽日午餐<br />\n沖完涼上下網  10點半訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：毒絲"},{"pid":"8ec11afcbc906dbff8545d7e27fdda9977ec5f03","tid":475771,"uid":12568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:48:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0213cc1362d142f8825cf776c4cbe170326023c3","tid":475771,"uid":116158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T16:14:44.000Z","msg":"奴工被說服的「work life balance」。。。<br />\n我上司講完呢個term真係想屌9佢，懷疑佢都比佢以前上司洗腦<br />\nILO 有一個建議標準，例如一星期上班少於48小時<br />\n仲有，工時一部分，人工咁低，想點比我balance我個life呀"},{"pid":"27494918f9a01743a06fa6eef7c88e35fc8544c6","tid":475771,"uid":124245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T17:02:27.000Z","msg":"我d同事覺得做到七點去做人個gym十點繼續做叫work life balance"}]}